50563 51437 exon
53952 54582 exon
54583 54882 UTR

< 70608 70751 MIR1289-1-201
70608 70751 exon

> 72252 91400 CEP250-202-cut3':44534bp
72252 72405 UTR
74958 75028 UTR
76637 76759 UTR
78919 79021 UTR
79022 79207 exon
